{"word":"G718 - ἁρμόζω - harmózō - har-mod'-zo - Espouse","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἁρμόζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">harmózō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">har-mod'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Espouse</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நியமி"},{"paragraph":"1. to join, to fit together of marriage"},{"paragraph":"2. to betroth a daughter to anyone"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G719 - ἁρμός - harmós - har-mos'/719\">G719</a>; to <i>joint</i>, that is, (figuratively) to <i>woo</i> (reflexively to <i>betroth</i>): - espouse.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}